      "title": "Special Notification of Parliament",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Parliamentary Secretary General Thammika Dasanayake has officially announced today (16) that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has resigned from the presidency of Sri Lanka effective July 14.",
        "This announcement was made when the Parliament met today at 10 am under the leadership of Speaker Mahinda Yaba Abeywardhana."
      ],
